distinct energy levels

188
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:58,190
and these energy levels
are labelled by magnetic

189
00:10:58,190 --> 00:11:00,720
quantum numbers, lower case m,

190
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:05,750
which can vary from minus i
